[{"location":"#TKM3D","page":"Home","title":"TKM3D","text":"Documentation for TKM3D.\n\n","category":"section"},{"location":"#TKM3D._ltkm3dd_eval-Tuple{AbstractMatrix{<:Real}, AbstractVector{<:Real}, AbstractMatrix{<:Real}, Function, Real, Real, Real}","page":"Home","title":"TKM3D._ltkm3dd_eval","text":"_ltkm3dd_eval(sources, charges, targets, windowhat, lw, kmax, eps;\n              need_grad=false, return_selfconst=false)\n\nEvaluate the discrete long-range TKM potential, and optionally the gradient, at targets for 3 x N source and target layouts.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#TKM3D.estimate_kcut3dc-Tuple{AbstractMatrix{<:Real}}","page":"Home","title":"TKM3D.estimate_kcut3dc","text":"estimate_kcut3dc(sources; charges, tol, eps=1e-12)\n\nEstimate the smallest radial spectral cutoff kcut such that the relative pointwise tail of the type-1 NUFFT spectrum satisfies\n\nmax_{|q| > kcut} |F(q)| / max_q |F(q)| < tol\n\nusing a Nyquist-limited anisotropic mode box inferred from the average positive source-coordinate gaps on each axis.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#TKM3D.ltkm3dc-Tuple{Real, AbstractMatrix{<:Real}}","page":"Home","title":"TKM3D.ltkm3dc","text":"ltkm3dc(eps, sources; charges, targets=nothing, pg=0, pgt=0, kmax=nothing)\n\nContinuous free-space Laplace TKM evaluator with arbitrary source points and preweighted quadrature masses.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"},{"location":"#TKM3D.ltkm3dd-Tuple{Real, AbstractMatrix{<:Real}}","page":"Home","title":"TKM3D.ltkm3dd","text":"ltkm3dd(eps, sources; charges, targets=nothing, pg=0, pgt=0, windowhat, lw, kmax)\n\nFMM3D-style interface for the discrete Laplace TKM long-range evaluator. Only charge sources are supported; dipole inputs are not implemented.\n\n\n\n\n\n","category":"method"}]
